The paper describes a framework for stream data mining, which involves machine learning and data science techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the framework includes methods for computer vision (cs.CV) and software engineering (cs.SE) for development and testing.
